HEADWORD: Pollan
<hw>Pol"lan</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. Gael.
<ets>pollag</ets> a kind of fish.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A lake
whitefish (<spn>Coregonus pollan</spn>), native of Ireland. In
appearance it resembles a herring.</def>⟦br⟧
